#  _compile-typst-site — compile-typst-site: command-line static
#                       site generator using Typst as the
#                       templating engine (Wade Cheng)
#
#  Source-direct extraction from
#    https://github.com/wade-cheng/compile-typst-site/blob/main/src/internals/config.rs (onlyargs Args struct)
#    https://github.com/wade-cheng/compile-typst-site/blob/main/Cargo.toml (bin: compile-typst-site, depends onlyargs)
