#  CLOSEST relative; both ultra-minimal but pico-args uses
#  `args.value_from_str("--flag")?` imperative-pull while
#  onlyargs uses `match arg.to_str()` loop), R404 Rust matklad/
#  xflags (declarative MACRO block syntax), R407 Rust blyxxyz/
#  lexopt (MINIMAL iterator-based pull parser), R410 Rust
#  murarth/gumdrop (zero-dep derive-macro), R413 Rust docopt/
#  docopt.rs (USAGE-STRING-IS-SPEC), R416 Rust rust-lang/
#  getopts (OFFICIAL POSIX-getopt(3) port), R420 Rust
#  ksk001100/seahorse (Cobra-for-Rust chained-builder), R427
#  Rust tanakh/argopt (function-as-CLI proc-macro), R430 Rust
#  killercup/quicli (batteries-included educational framework),
